c: 58
v: 12
t: "ya 'ayuha aladhin sddaqu allah warasulah waeamiluu bshreh, 'iidha 'aradtum 'an tukllimu rasul allah salaa allah ealayh wasalam srrana baynakum wbynh, fqddimu qabl dhlk sadaqat li'ahl alhajt, dhlk khayr lakum lamaa fih min althwab, wazka liqulubikum min almathm, fa'iin lam tajiduu ma ttsdqwn bih fala haraj elykm; fa'iina allah ghafur lieibadih almwmnyn, rahim bhm"